abstract: Quixey, a search engine for apps, announced on Thursday that it had raised a $50 million financing round led by Alibaba.
snippet: Quixey, a search engine for apps, announced on Thursday that it had raised a $50 million financing round led by Alibaba.
lead_paragraph: The Chinese Internet company Alibaba Group wears a number of hats, with commerce sites, a payment system and a search engine.

headline.main: Alibaba Invests in a Search Engine for Apps
